{"word":"ἀπόκρυφος","slug":"ἀπόκρυφος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπόκρυφος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀποκρύπτω'><el>ἀποκρύπτω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>hidden, concealed</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>ἐν ἀποκρύφωι</el> <i>in secret</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>concealed from, unknown to</i> one, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>obscure, hard to understand</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}